<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is my first book read in French and I recommend it to anyone learning the language and wanting to go a bit further. I read it on my kindle and th<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is my first book read in French and I recommend it to anyone learning the language and wanting to go a bit further. I read it on my kindle and the built-in dictionary and translation feature helped at times where I felt a bit stuck. Now looking forward to part 2<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
