        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1780738148" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16043460017408074063">This is a classic collection of stories in French about Nicolas and his inapt parents. Idyllic about life in the late 50s and early 60s, they are full of humour and tales of growing up. In France, they are like the equivalent of Tom Sawyer and Huck Finn.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


