<span id="freeTextContainer4989372645040868551">I started reading this with my French tutor last fall, but I finally got around to finish all of the episodes. There are laugh-out-loud moments in this book, but I was especially stunned by all of the violence in it. I didn&apos;t catch that so much the last time I read a Petit Nicolas book. I guess little kids are like that, but it was strange. <br/><br/>Great, though, especially if you&apos;re looking for a enjoyable book that isn&apos;t too hard in French. </span>
