              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17832004025758617399">This certainly wins the prize for the Sweetest Book I Have Ever Read!<br/><i>Le Petit Nicolas</i> was such a joy to read; it is a children’s book that anyone (child or adult) can connect to. Stories of young friendship, comedy, and growing up are at their best in this collection. Pure, pure delight!<br/><br/>I have heard that this is a bit of a classic in France so that makes me even happier.<br/><br/>I would recommend this strongly to any French speaker/reader!</span>

          </span>
